Name: Last Group Out
About the game: Last Group Out is an casual top down shooter that takes place in an abandoned country, torn by economic collapse. Inspired by 'Escape from Tarkov' and 'The Escapists'. Go scavenge - Travel to a hostile land and collect all you can before the timer runs out. - Use this time to level up your character and build your wealth. Collect loot - Find items to help you in your journey. - Sell items to gain better weapons and equipment. Hone your skills - Level up your character by defeating enemies, looting items, and completing quests. - Unlock new Weapons and Equipment by leveling up or defeating bosses. - Level up your weapons to gain special buffs. Stop, Look, Listen, Smell - Danger lies around every corner, use stealth and your survivalist senses to stay alive. Play alone or with friends - Go in solo, or with up to 3 friends to complete quests and level up your character.
